{"tid":1598874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署要人！促請澳洲國會制裁侵害香港人權者！Petitions to the Australian Parliament","createTime":"2019-09-27T16:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:28:18.000Z","uid":264380,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"85ef4579c63c1f3bf0216a454eff35d8e25a19b4","tid":1598874,"uid":264380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"傳說中連登係有英語系人士mon post，所以中英並用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> To those who want to support Hongkongers, please spare us some time to sign this petition 全球手足望呢邊<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\nPetition for the Senate of Australia to Impose Sanctions on Persons Suppressing Human Rights in HK (Open to <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">EVERYONE</span>, including those who are not Australians)<br />\n促請澳洲制裁打壓香港人權者（非澳洲居民亦可簽署）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/the-senate-of-australia-impose-sanctions-on-persons-found-to-be-suppressing-human-rights-in-hong-kong-df999fe5-3d9f-434b-8f58-d0840619a046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fthe-senate-of-australia-impose-sanctions-on-persons-found-to-be-suppressing-human-rights-in-hong-kong-df999fe5-3d9f-434b-8f58-d0840619a046&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=f6648674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/the-senate-of-australia-impose-sanctions-on-persons-found-to-be-suppressing-human-rights-in-hong-kong-df999fe5-3d9f-434b-8f58-d0840619a046</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Other ways to help Hongkongers if you are an Australian resident or citizen<br />\n澳洲手足仲有其他方法幫手<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\nPetition for the the House of Representatives to bring the true condition of Hong Kong&rsquo;s predicament to the United Nations Human Rights Council (For Australian <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">residents and citizens</span> only)<br />\n聯署促請澳洲眾議院向聯合國人權理事會如實反映香港困局（僅限澳洲居民及公民）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_sign?id=EN1029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aph.gov.au%2Fpetition_sign%3Fid%3DEN1029&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=0f9f345a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_sign?id=EN1029</a><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\nPetition for the House of Representatives to add human rights clauses to its free trade agreement (FTA) with Hong Kong (For Australian <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">residents and citizens</span> only)<br />\n聯署促請澳洲眾議院於香港與澳洲《自由貿易協定》加入人權條款（僅限澳洲居民及公民）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_sign?id=EN1032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aph.gov.au%2Fpetition_sign%3Fid%3DEN1032&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=60d037c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_sign?id=EN1032</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 澳洲版人權法！！！</span></span><br />\nLetter for the MPs to introduce the International Human Rights and Corruption (Magnitsky Sanctions) Bill to the parliament (For Australian <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">citizens</span> only)<br />\n請願信促請眾議院議員就International Human Rights and Corruption (Magnitsky Sanctions) Bill提案（僅限澳洲公民）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2664406130276175?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F2664406130276175%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=82cb8e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2664406130276175?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nThank you for supporting our fight for freedom and democracy. Free Hong Kong, democracy now!"},{"pid":"c4ec141b6182c38dedf1b26a535e01c9309cb2c5","tid":1598874,"uid":264380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"推⋯⋯唔倒"},{"pid":"e48ba75b5657f13e2aab9575125ecb5701fea6f6","tid":1598874,"uid":22637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"推 得到"},{"pid":"f4e2a2d1f672332bc72b892239ecaeaa8f958a8b","tid":1598874,"uid":78780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ba8b8b69bf517034009167e00704769e1e23eb","tid":1598874,"uid":78780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48ba75b5657f13e2aab9575125ecb5701fea6f6","tid":1598874,"uid":22637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"推 得到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e647f9b07e5dfa45cc84936645486cd88cbea","tid":1598874,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d334ce699d8549de4b4fe12365735faa49e7670","tid":1598874,"uid":78780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b7d9f1750c76efb5718de3a345b7c01cda6fb5","tid":1598874,"uid":91087,"like":0,"dislike